products.name: Legato White 3 Door Mirrored Wardrobe
description: The Legato 3 Door Mirrored Wardrobe features a contemporary style with a unique handle-less design and a high gloss finish.
Constructed from high quality components this 3 door mirrored wardrobe makes for a practical and stylish storage solution for your bedroom.
Part of the Legato range, this wardrobe is available in a variety of styles and will make the perfect addition to your living space creating a fresh new look.

products.name: Ethan White 4 Door Wardrobe with Mirrors
description: This stylish wardrobe features profiled doors with shaker style metal handles. Including high quality components and multi-adjustable hinges this wardrobe isn't just practical but features a beautifully designed grain effect finish with a crisp White coloured coat, perfect for almost any bedroom.

products.name: Ethan Graphite 4 Door Wardrobe with Mirrors
description: This stylish wardrobe features profiled doors with shaker style metal handles. Including high quality components and multi-adjustable hinges this wardrobe isn't just practical but features a beautifully designed grain effect finish with a crisp White coloured coat, perfect for almost any bedroom.

products.name: Nevada 4 Door 2 Drawer Oyster Mirrored Wardrobe
description: The Nevada 4 Door 2 Drawer Mirrored Wardrobe features a contemporary design owing to the gloss finished front which contrasts perfectly with the light oak veneers. The Nevada has your storage needs covered thanks to the 2 drawers, top shelf and hanging space from the metal rail.

products.name: Lucy Cane Grey Gents Wardrobe
description: Inspired by vintage French styling, the Lucy Cane range is elegantly crafted to provide a perfect statement piece for any living space.
Finished in an aged painted colourway with natural lacquered coating, this stunning range features a woven cane design and turned legs.
Designed with a full-length hanging rail and fixed bottom shelf, this wardrobe also features dark round metal handles and smooth runners with pull-out stop for added convenience.

products.name: Lynx Walnut and Black Triple Wardrobe with 2 Drawers
description: This sturdy and spacious wardrobe consists of an internal top shelf, hanging rail and shelving behind three doors, plus two drawers for additional storage. It combines walnut and black high gloss for a striking, modern look which is sure to stand out. This three door wardrobe features silver finish plastic handles, a mirrored panel and smooth, metal drawer runners.

products.name: Ellum Black Sliding Wardrobe
description: Designed to complement contemporary interiors, the Dallas 2 Door High Gloss Sliding Wardrobe is an eye-catching storage solution for your bedroom.
This spacious wardrobe features two smooth, sliding doors with high gloss fronts.
Inside you will find two adjustable hanging rails and two adjustable shelves so you can personalise your storage space.

products.name: Ellum Oak Sliding Wardrobe
description: The Ellum Oak Double Sliding Wardrobe is a spacious, stylish and practical wardrobe for your bedroom.
With adjustable shelves, a textured 3D finish and metal handles, the Ellum will have all your bedroom storage needs taken care of.
